TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Uh... Me ask questions?
Goodbye.
That cult preying on Neverwinter - know anything about it?
Text: 네버윈터를 노리는 사이비 교단 - 아는 거 있어요?

TextEng: Actually I'm more interested in local affairs...
Text: 사실 이 지역 일에 더 관심이 있어요...

TextEng: How long have you farmed here?
Anything interesting about these parts?
Text: 이 근처에 뭔가 흥미로운 거 있어요?

TextEng: Yuh, da cult. What you know of it?
Uh, what 'bout stuff in this area?
Text: 어, 이 지역 일은 뭐 있어?

TextEng: How long you farm 'round here?
Uh, there be any odd stories 'bout this place?
Did anything else stand out about him?
Text: 그 사람한테서 다른 특이한 점은 없었나요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Why do you say "as good as gone?"
Any other stuff about strange guy?
Text: 그 이상한 놈 다른 거 있어?

TextEng: Tell me one of your father-in-law's stories.
Actually, I'm more interested in a job, if you know of anything.
Text: 사실, 일거리가 있다면 더 관심 있는데요.

TextEng: Are there any places you think I should visit?
Yuh, tell me story den...
Me want work.
There be other places to go 'round here?
Text: 이 근처 다른 갈 데 있어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, telling me won't do any harm.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. Will hurt nobody.
I'm curious about some recent events...
There be stuff happening lately, yuh?
I have some other questions.
Me have other question.
Can I ask you some directions?
Uh, me lost. You give directions, yuh?
Text: 어, 나 길 잃었어. 길 알려줘, 응?

TextEng: Where does the west road lead?
Where does the east road lead?
Is there a place where I might rest nearby?
Where that west road go?
Where that east road go?
Me need place to buy stuff.
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
Me have other question.
I need some more directions.
Me need more directions.
A story, is it? I'd love to hear it...
Yuh, tell me story, then.
Could you answer some other questions for me?
Text: 다른 질문도 대답해 주실 수 있어요?

TextEng: Me have other questions... You answer, yuh?
Text: 나 다른 질문 있어... 대답해줄 거지, 응?

TextEng: How come?
Yuh?
Who is Pete O'Deel?
Who Pete O'Deel?
Trouble with wolves?
Wolf trouble?
Who are the O'Deels?
Who them O'Deels?
What are your thoughts on the O'Deel lass?
What you think 'bout that 'Deel girlie?
